{
  "slug": "netbox-compose",
  "kind": "compose",
  "metadata": {
    "name": "NetBox",
    "description": "Network infrastructure management (IPAM/DCIM) and automation source of truth. Manages IP addresses, circuits, devices, racks, cables, and other network infrastructure components.",
    "guide": "## Overview\nNetwork infrastructure management (IPAM/DCIM) and automation source of truth. Manages IP addresses, circuits, devices, racks, cables, and other network infrastructure components.\n\n## How to Use\nThis template renders `compose.yaml` and `.env` as files.\n\n1. Decide on service names, ports, volumes, credentials, and optional integrations before rendering the stack.\n2. Fill in the required variables first, then enable optional sections such as Traefik, metrics, or extra services only when needed.\n3. Render the Compose project, review the generated files, and start it with Docker Compose in the target directory.\n\n## Variable Guide\n### Database\n- `database_name`: Name of the database; optional; default: netbox.\n- `database_user`: Username for the database; optional; default: netbox.\n- `database_host`: Hostname used for Database; required; shown when: database_external=true.\n- `database_password`: Password for the database; required.\n- `redis_password`: Redis password for authentication; required.\n- `database_external`: Use external database; optional; default: false.\n\n### Email\n- `email_host`: Hostname used for SMTP Server; required.\n- `email_port`: Port used for SMTP Server; required; default: 25.\n- `email_username`: Username for the smtp; required.\n- `email_password`: Password for the smtp; required.\n- `email_from`: IP address to use for the from email; required.\n- `email_enabled`: Enable email integration; optional; default: false.\n- `email_encryption`: The email encryption type; optional; default: tls.\n\n### General\n- `service_name`: Name of the service; optional; default: netbox.\n- `container_timezone`: Timezone used inside the container; optional.\n- `restart_policy`: Policy used for Restart; required; default: unless-stopped; options: unless-stopped, always, on-failure, no.\n\n### NetBox Configuration\n- `netbox_metrics_enabled`: Enable Prometheus metrics endpoint; optional; default: false.\n- `netbox_secret_key`: Value used for the netbox configuration settings; required.\n\n### Ports\n- `ports_http`: Host port for HTTP; optional; default: 8000.\n\n### Traefik\n- `traefik_enabled`: Enable Traefik integration; optional; default: false.\n- `traefik_host`: Hostname used for Traefik; optional.\n- `traefik_domain`: Domain used for Traefik; required.\n- `traefik_network`: Network used for Traefik; required; default: traefik.\n- `traefik_tls_enabled`: Enable Traefik TLS; optional; default: false.\n- `traefik_tls_certresolver`: Traefik Tls Certresolver; required; default: cloudflare; shown when: traefik_tls_enabled=true.\n\n## References\n- [NetBox](https://netbox.dev/)\n- [Documentation](https://docs.netbox.dev/)\n- [GitHub](https://github.com/netbox-community/netbox)\n\n## Next Steps\nLog in with your initial admin user:\n```bash\nUsername: admin\nPassword: admin\n```",
    "tags": [
      "traefik",
      "database",
      "email"
    ],
    "template_version": "v4.5.2",
    "icon": {
      "provider": "selfhst",
      "id": "netbox"
    },
    "draft": false
  },
  "variables": [
    {
      "title": "Database",
      "name": "database",
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "database_name",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Database Name",
          "required": false,
          "default": "netbox",
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "netbox"
          },
          "description": "Name of the database."
        },
        {
          "name": "database_user",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Database User",
          "required": false,
          "default": "netbox",
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "netbox"
          },
          "description": "Username for the database."
        },
        {
          "name": "database_host",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Database Host",
          "required": true,
          "needs": [
            "database_external=true"
          ],
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "postgres"
          },
          "description": "Hostname used for Database."
        },
        {
          "name": "database_password",
          "type": "secret",
          "title": "Database Password",
          "required": true,
          "description": "Password for the database.",
          "config": {
            "autogenerated": true
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "redis_password",
          "type": "secret",
          "title": "Redis Password",
          "required": true,
          "description": "Redis password for authentication",
          "config": {
            "autogenerated": true
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "database_external",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "External Database",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Use external database"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Email",
      "toggle": "email_enabled",
      "name": "email",
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "email_host",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "SMTP server hostname",
          "required": true,
          "description": "Hostname used for SMTP Server."
        },
        {
          "name": "email_port",
          "type": "int",
          "title": "SMTP server port",
          "required": true,
          "default": 25,
          "description": "Port used for SMTP Server.",
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "25"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "email_username",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "SMTP username",
          "required": true,
          "description": "Username for the smtp."
        },
        {
          "name": "email_password",
          "type": "secret",
          "title": "SMTP password",
          "required": true,
          "description": "Password for the smtp."
        },
        {
          "name": "email_from",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "From email address",
          "required": true,
          "description": "IP address to use for the from email."
        },
        {
          "name": "email_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Email",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable email integration"
        },
        {
          "name": "email_encryption",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Encryption",
          "required": false,
          "default": "tls",
          "description": "The email encryption type",
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "tls"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "General",
      "name": "general",
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "service_name",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Service Name",
          "required": false,
          "default": "netbox",
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "netbox"
          },
          "description": "Name of the service."
        },
        {
          "name": "container_timezone",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Container Timezone",
          "required": false,
          "description": "Timezone used inside the container."
        },
        {
          "name": "restart_policy",
          "type": "enum",
          "title": "Restart Policy",
          "required": true,
          "default": "unless-stopped",
          "config": {
            "options": [
              "unless-stopped",
              "always",
              "on-failure",
              "no"
            ]
          },
          "description": "Policy used for Restart."
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "NetBox Configuration",
      "name": "netbox",
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "netbox_metrics_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Metrics",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable Prometheus metrics endpoint"
        },
        {
          "name": "netbox_secret_key",
          "type": "secret",
          "title": "Secret Key",
          "required": true,
          "description": "Value used for the netbox configuration settings.",
          "config": {
            "autogenerated": true
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Ports",
      "name": "ports",
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "ports_http",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "HTTP Port",
          "required": false,
          "default": 8000,
          "description": "Host port for HTTP",
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "8000"
          }
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "title": "Traefik",
      "name": "traefik",
      "toggle": "traefik_enabled",
      "items": [
        {
          "name": "traefik_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "Traefik",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable Traefik integration"
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_host",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Host",
          "required": false,
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "netbox"
          },
          "description": "Hostname used for Traefik."
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_domain",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Domain",
          "required": true,
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "home.arpa"
          },
          "description": "Domain used for Traefik."
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_entrypoint",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Entrypoint",
          "required": true,
          "default": "web",
          "description": "Entrypoint name.",
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "web"
          }
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_network",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Network",
          "required": true,
          "default": "traefik",
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "traefik"
          },
          "description": "Network used for Traefik."
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_tls_enabled",
          "type": "bool",
          "title": "TLS",
          "required": false,
          "default": false,
          "description": "Enable Traefik TLS"
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_tls_entrypoint",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "TLS Entrypoint",
          "required": true,
          "default": "websecure",
          "description": "Entrypoint name.",
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "websecure"
          },
          "needs": [
            "traefik_tls_enabled=true"
          ]
        },
        {
          "name": "traefik_tls_certresolver",
          "type": "str",
          "title": "Cert Resolver",
          "required": true,
          "default": "cloudflare",
          "config": {
            "placeholder": "cloudflare"
          },
          "description": "Traefik Tls Certresolver",
          "needs": [
            "traefik_tls_enabled=true"
          ]
        }
      ]
    }
  ]
}
